import sys

n, m = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().split()]
a = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().split()]
ans = 0
for i in range(n):
    a[i] -= m
    if a[i] < 0:
        ans = i
print(ans + 1)

import sys

n, m = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
a = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))
ans = 0
for i in range(n):
    a[i] -= m
    if a[i] < 0:
        ans = i
print(ans + 1)
